nen zur Seite.\nWir helfen unseren Kunden bei der Logistik, Produktadministration, Konstruktion und dem Einkauf. Die langjährigen Erfahrungen des Blechwerk-Teams sind der Garant für das umfassende Leistungsspektrum, das wir unseren Kunden bieten.\n\nWir freuen uns auf Ihren Besuch!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"http://patrickz.no-ip.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Home-bild-unten1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-194 size-full\" src=\"http://patrickz.no-ip.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Home-bild-unten1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"511\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://patrickz.no-ip.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/pr-gruen-design-1502.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-338\" src=\"http://patrickz.no-ip.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/pr-gruen-design-1502.png\" alt=\"pr-gruen-design-150\" width=\"150\" height=\"126\" /></a>\n\n</div>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-autosave-v1','','','2014-05-29 17:25:55','2014-05-29 15:25:55','',8,'http://patrickz.no-ip.org/?p=182',0,'revision','',0),(183,1,'2014-05-23 17:35:32','2014-05-23 15:35:32','<div id=\"mmm_col2ContStart\">\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"113,85,82\"]\r\n\r\n</div>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-revision-v1','','','2014-05-23 17:35:32','2014-05-23 15:35:32','',8,'http://patrickz.no-ip.org/?p=183',0,'revision','',0),(184,1,'2014-05-23 17:36:26','2014-05-23 15:36:26','<div id=\"mmm_col2ContStart\">\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"113,82,85\"]\r\n\r\n</div>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-revision-v1','','','2014-05-23 17:36:26','2014-05-23 15:36:26','',8,'http://patrickz.no-ip.org/?p=184',0,'revision','',0),(185,1,'2014-05-23 17:37:23','2014-05-23 15:37:23','<div id=\"mmm_col2ContStart\">\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"113,82,85\"]\r\n\r\n</div>','','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-revision-v1','','','2014-05-23 17:37:23','2014-05-23 15:37:23','',8,'http://patrickz.no-ip.org/?p=185',0,'revision','',0),(186,1,'2014-05-23 17:37:38','2014-05-23